title: Eddie Murphy - Raw (Stand-up comedy) 1987
description:
As said in the title, this is an ipod-quality video of Murphy's second stand-up comedy program called Raw.

He rants about the press and their lack of politeness regarding stars, about relationships, the small oddities about men and women, social changes in the 1980s and more.

Trust me, it's hilarious (for men as well as for women)!

Video quality is a little on the rough side due to the format and its production age, but the most important element is him talking anyway. 

Enjoy!
